      "comment": "CHILLI CRUMPET (3) flew the lids from out wide with a slick early split but ran over at the finish when a narrow fourth (22.20) over 390m at this track. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Has ability and looks hard to stop. FAYE VALENTINE (2) beaten last start over the 390m at Warrnambool but finished in the minors in a solid 22.12. Top win latest and can measure up again. ZENI BALE (1) missed the frame latest but had been racing well prior to that including a Grade 4/5 win two back (22.50) at this track. Expecting significant improvement this line-up. PAW KARSON (8) has been a model of consistency and deserves plenty of thought.",
